	"name": "Intellectual",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/commodities/biological/organ-brain-pink-purple.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have taken up an even broader and deeper program of study than most scholars, and have reaped a harvest of knowledge. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Intelligence, or Wisdom increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with two languages of your choice.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with a total of two skills and/or tools you are not proficient with.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die with a skill you are proficient with. The maximum expertise die for the chosen skill becomes a d12.</p></li><li><p>You gain a total of four skill specialties among skills you are proficient with. They do not count against your skill specialties known.</p></li><li><p>Your exertion pool increases by 1.</p></li></ul>",
